188
00:10:10,240 --> 00:10:12,260
and the previous quick attacks,

189
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,640
your combination

190
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,660
will be unbeatable.

191
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:19,900
Are you sure?

192
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,780
It's also about quick attacks.

193
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:24,780
We're playing beach volleyball, not indoors.

194
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:27,560
The requirements for jumping ability

195
00:10:27,560 --> 00:10:28,780
and speed are very high.

196
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:31,020
