spent five or six days

203
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:44,460
finding this technique.

204
00:10:44,760 --> 00:10:46,040
It's challenging,

205
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:46,920
but

206
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:47,980
we believe

207
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:50,100
