238
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,900
are actually the same.

239
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:18,560
It's just whether there's a net

240
00:12:18,560 --> 00:12:19,400
or blocking.

241
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:20,820
The better your hang-time,

242
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,540
the stronger your spike.

243
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,320
So, practicing hang-time

244
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,580
is like perfecting

245
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:28,680
a powerful spike, right?

246
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:29,520
Exactly.

247
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,360
Now, let's analyze

248
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,500
