249
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,640
Li Guoduo is the receiver.

250
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,800
After receiving it, pass it to the setter.

251
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,620
At this moment,

252
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:40,000
you move to the outside,

253
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,940
making others think you'll attack from there.

254
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,380
The setter is crucial at this point.

255
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:47,100
Your timing and the force on the ball

256
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:50,020
should create a high arc ball
to spread the play.

257
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,560
Li Guoduo quickly

258
00:12:51,560 --> 00:12:53,280
cuts to this position

259
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:54,260
to spike and score.

260
00:12:54,560 --> 00:12:56,360
This also requires your hang-time

261
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,620
and core strength.

262
00:12:58,160 --> 00:12:59,240
I understand now.

263
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:01,240
